2 Simple Maps Example

state <- map_data("state")
county <- map_data("county")
bat_point <- data.frame("x" = -87.46544, "y" = 36.58861)
tn <- county %>% 
  filter(region=="tennessee")
ky <- county %>% 
  filter(region=="kentucky")
montco <- county %>% 
  filter(region=="tennessee") %>% 
  filter(subregion=="montgomery")
stewco <- county %>% 
  filter(region=="tennessee") %>% 
  filter(subregion=="stewart")
triggco <- county %>% 
  filter(region=="kentucky") %>% 
  filter(subregion=="trigg")
chrisco <- county %>% 
  filter(region=="kentucky") %>% 
  filter(subregion=="christian")
ggplot() + geom_polygon(data = state, aes(x=long, y = lat, group = group),
                        fill = "white", color="black") + 
           geom_polygon(data = tn, aes(x=long, y = lat, group = group),
                        fill = "gray", color="black") + 
           geom_polygon(data = ky, aes(x=long, y = lat, group = group),
                        fill = "gray", color="black") + 
           geom_polygon(data = montco, aes(x=long, y = lat, group = group),
                        fill = "purple", color="black") + 
           geom_polygon(data = stewco, aes(x=long, y = lat, group = group),
                        fill = "purple", color="black") + 
           geom_polygon(data = triggco, aes(x=long, y = lat, group = group),
                        fill = "purple", color="black") +
           geom_polygon(data = chrisco, aes(x=long, y = lat, group = group),
                        fill = "purple", color="black") +
           geom_point(data = bat_point, aes(x=x,y=y), color="black") +
  coord_fixed(xlim = c(-91, -81),  ylim = c(34, 39), ratio = 1.2) + 
  xlab("Longitude") + ylab("Latitude") + ggtitle("Fort Campbell IGSA")

3 Interactive Map Example

leaflet(pesu873OGR) %>% 
  addTiles() %>% 
  addMarkers(popup = pesu873OGR@data$Name)

3.1 Adding Polygons

leaflet(pesu873OGR) %>% 
  addTiles() %>%
  addPolygons(hrOGR, 
              lng = hr_poly$X, 
              lat = hr_poly$Y,
              fillColor = "grey",
              color = "black") %>%
  addCircleMarkers(popup = pesu873OGR@data$Name,
                   weight = 2,
                   color = "grey",
                   fillColor = "red",
                   fillOpacity = 0.7)
hrOGR@data$Description <- c("PESU 873")

3.3 Interactive FTC Map

leaflet() %>% 
  setView(lng = -87.608371, lat = 36.621813, zoom = 13) %>%
  addWMSTiles("https://basemap.nationalmap.gov/arcgis/services/USGSTopo/MapServer/WmsServer", layers = "0") %>%
  addMiniMap(zoomLevelOffset = -4) %>%
  addScaleBar()

3.4 Multi Background PESU Map

leaflet(pesu873OGR) %>% 
  addTiles(group = "OSM")%>%
  addProviderTiles(providers$CartoDB.Positron, group = "CartoDB") %>%
  addProviderTiles(providers$Esri.NatGeoWorldMap, group = "NatGeo") %>%
  addProviderTiles(providers$Esri.WorldImagery, group = "ESRI") %>%
    setView(lng = -87.608371, lat = 36.621813, zoom = 17) %>%
  addPolygons(pesu873OGR, 
              lng = hr_poly$X, 
              lat = hr_poly$Y,
              label = hrOGR@data$Description,
              fillColor = "grey",
              color = "white") %>%
  addCircleMarkers(popup = pesu873OGR@data$Name,
                   label = pesu873OGR@data$Description,
                   group = "PESU",
                   weight = 2,
                   color = "grey",
                   fillColor = "purple",
                   fillOpacity = 0.7) %>%
  addLayersControl(
    baseGroups = c("OSM", "CartoDB", "NatGeo", "ESRI"),
    options = layersControlOptions(collapsed = FALSE),
    overlayGroups = "PESU")
